          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span><span>/customer-support-agent
</span></span><span>├── README.md              ← Main showcase document
</span><span>├── system-prompt.md       ← The prompt that drives the agent
</span><span>├── knowledge-base/        ← Folder with FAQs, escalation rules
</span><span>├── sample-conversations/  ← Real test scenarios showing it working
</span><span>└── evaluation-criteria.md ← How you'd measure success</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>The README is the most important file</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">It's the first thing anyone sees. It should read like a mini case study:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Problem statement</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Agent design decisions</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Limitations you identified</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">What you'd improve with more resources</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>The honest caveat</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The repository itself won't impress anyone if the content inside is thin. The system prompt and documentation need to reflect genuine thinking about customer support agent design. That's the actual work.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Suggested order of steps</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Build the agent first in Claude.ai Projects</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Test it properly with realistic scenarios</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Document what you built</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Then put it on GitHub</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Want to start with designing the actual agent? That's the foundation everything else depends on.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
