<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Typing the <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/</code> will automatically create the folder</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Paste this content:</p>
