n class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> FAQ - Payments and Purchases</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Overview</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>This document covers the most common payment and purchase issues 
</span><span>reported by players at Tier 1 support level.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q1: A player was charged but did not receive their purchased items.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Likely causes:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Transaction processed but delivery delayed
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> App was closed before delivery completed
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Temporary server-side issue
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Ask the player to restart the app and check again.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Ask for the transaction ID or receipt from their payment provider.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Verify the purchase against available order records.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> If items are still missing after restart, escalate with transaction ID attached.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Do not</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> promise manual delivery without verification.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q2: A player's payment failed but they were charged.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Likely causes:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Bank pre-authorization that was not released
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Double charge due to a retry attempt
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Advise the player to check with their bank - pre-authorizations 
</span></span><span>   typically release within 3-5 business days.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> If the charge is confirmed and no purchase exists on the account, 
</span></span><span>   escalate to billing specialist immediately.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Collect: transaction ID, date, amount, payment method type.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Do not</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> issue refund commitments at Tier 1.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q3: A player wants a refund.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Policy:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Refunds are not handled at Tier 1 level.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Acknowledge the request professionally.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Escalate to billing team with full transaction details.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Inform the player that refund eligibility is reviewed case by case 
</span></span><span>   and provide expected response timeframe.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Do not</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> indicate whether a refund will or will not be approved.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q4: A player's purchase option is not showing or the store is not loading.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Likely causes:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> App cache issue
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Regional store availability
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Temporary backend issue
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Ask the player to clear app cache and restart.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Ask what device and OS version they are using.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> If the issue persists across multiple restarts, collect device info 
</span></span><span>   and escalate to technical team.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q5: A player was charged multiple times for the same item.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Treat as high priority.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Collect all transaction IDs and dates.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Escalate immediately to billing specialist.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Inform the player their case is being reviewed urgently.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Do not</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> attempt to resolve duplicate charges at Tier 1.</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
