          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="text-text-500 font-small p-3.5 pb-0">markdown</div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-markdown" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;"><span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">#</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> FAQ - Account Access and Login</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Overview</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>This document covers the most common account access and login issues 
</span><span>reported by players at Tier 1 support level.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q1: A player cannot log into their account.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Likely causes:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Incorrect credentials
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Session timeout or token issue
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Server-side authentication issue
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Ask the player which login method they use (email, Facebook, 
</span></span><span>   Google, Apple ID, guest).
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Ask them to confirm they are using the correct credentials.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Ask them to try logging out fully and logging back in.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Ask them to clear app cache and retry.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">5.</span><span> If the issue persists, collect account details and escalate.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Do not</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> ask for passwords. Ever.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q2: A player forgot their password.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Direct them to the "Forgot Password" option on the login screen.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Confirm which email address is associated with the account.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Ask them to check spam/junk folders for the reset email.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> If the reset email is not arriving, collect their email address 
</span></span><span>   and escalate to account team.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q3: A player lost access to their guest account.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">This is a high-sensitivity issue.</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> Guest accounts are not tied 
</span></span><span>to an email or social login, making recovery difficult.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Ask if they have a Player ID or any in-game screenshots showing 
</span></span><span>   their account.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Ask what device they were playing on and whether they still have 
</span></span><span>   access to it.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Escalate immediately with all collected details.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Set clear expectations: recovery is not guaranteed without 
</span></span><span>   sufficient identifying information.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q4: A player's account was logged into by someone else / they </span><span>
</span></span><span>suspect unauthorized access.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Treat as high priority.</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Advise the player to change their password immediately if they 
</span></span><span>   still have access.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Advise them to revoke any connected third-party app permissions.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Escalate to the security team immediately with account details 
</span></span><span>   and a description of the suspected breach.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Do not investigate account access logs at Tier 1 level.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q5: A player wants to merge two accounts or transfer progress.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Policy:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Account merges and progress transfers are not handled at Tier 1.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Acknowledge the request.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Escalate to account specialist team with details of both accounts.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Inform the player that this process is reviewed case by case and 
</span></span><span>   set realistic timeframe expectations.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Q6: A player is being logged out repeatedly mid-session.</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Likely causes:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Unstable internet connection
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Session token expiry bug
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Device-specific issue
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Resolution steps:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Ask the player to check their internet connection stability.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Ask them to clear cache and reinstall if the issue persists.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Collect device model, OS version, and frequency of the issue.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> If multiple players report the same issue simultaneously, 
</span></span><span>   escalate as a potential server-side bug.</span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Commit it, then come back for <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">knowledge-base/escalation-rules.md</code>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
