n class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Escalation Rules</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Overview</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>This document defines when and how the agent escalates tickets 
</span><span>to specialist teams. Escalation accuracy is a key performance 
</span><span>metric for Tier 1 operations.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Core Escalation Principle</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>When in doubt, escalate. A wrongly escalated ticket costs less 
</span><span>than a wrongly handled one. Never attempt to resolve an issue 
</span><span>outside Tier 1 scope to avoid escalating.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Escalate Immediately - No Exceptions</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>The following issues must always be escalated without any 
</span><span>attempt at Tier 1 resolution:
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Issue Type </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Route To </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-header-row"></span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-line"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Account ban or suspension </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Trust &amp; Safety team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Fraud or chargeback dispute </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Billing specialist </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Duplicate charges </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Billing specialist </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Suspected unauthorized account access </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Security team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Legal or privacy requests (GDPR, data deletion) </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Legal/Compliance </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Player is abusive or threatening </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Senior agent or TL </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Bug affecting multiple players simultaneously </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Technical team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Escalate After Tier 1 Steps Failed</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>The following issues should first go through Tier 1 resolution 
</span><span>steps. If unresolved, escalate with full notes attached:
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Issue Type </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Route To </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-header-row"></span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-line"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Missing purchase items (verified transaction) </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Billing specialist </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Failed password reset </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Account team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Guest account recovery </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Account team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Persistent login issues after troubleshooting </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Technical team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Store not loading after cache clear and reinstall </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Technical team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Account merge or progress transfer request </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Account specialist </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Repeat contact on same unresolved issue </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Senior agent </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> How to Escalate</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Summarize the issue clearly in your escalation note.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Include all relevant details collected from the player:
</span></span><span><span>   </span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Player ID / username
</span></span><span><span>   </span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Device and OS version (if relevant)
</span></span><span><span>   </span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Transaction IDs (if relevant)
</span></span><span><span>   </span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Steps already attempted
</span></span><span><span>   </span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Any screenshots or evidence provided
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Set the correct priority level (standard / high / urgent).
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Inform the player their case has been escalated and provide 
</span></span><span>   a realistic response timeframe.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Priority Levels</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Priority </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> When to Use </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Expected Response Time </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-header-row"></span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-line"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Urgent </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Security breach, legal request, abusive player </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Immediate </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> High </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Duplicate charges, ban dispute, account breach </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Within 4 hours </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Standard </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> All other escalations </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Within 24-48 hours </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> What Not to Do When Escalating</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Do not promise outcomes (refunds, item restoration, unban).
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Do not tell the player who specifically will handle their case.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Do not escalate without collecting the minimum required information.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Do not close the ticket before confirming escalation was received.</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
