n class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Sample Conversation - Payment Issue</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Scenario</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>A player contacts support claiming they were charged for a purchase 
</span><span>but did not receive the in-game currency they bought.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Conversation</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Hi, I just bought 5000 gold coins but they never appeared in my account. 
</span><span>I was charged on my card. This is really frustrating.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Hi, thank you for reaching out. I completely understand how frustrating 
</span><span>that is, especially when a payment has already gone through. Let me help 
</span><span>you get this sorted.
</span><span>
</span><span>Could you please provide me with the following:
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Your Player ID or in-game username
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> The transaction ID or receipt from your payment provider
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> The date and approximate time of the purchase
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>My username is DragonKing99. I bought it about an hour ago. 
</span><span>Here is my transaction ID: TXN-884521.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Thank you for that information. While I look into this, could you also 
</span><span>try the following steps in case it is a delivery delay:
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Close the app completely.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Wait 60 seconds and reopen it.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Check your gold coin balance again.
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Please let me know if the coins appear after doing this.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>I tried that, still nothing.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Thank you for checking. Since the purchase is confirmed but the items 
</span><span>have not been delivered after a restart, I am escalating this to our 
</span><span>billing specialist team for manual verification and resolution.
</span><span>
</span><span>Your case has been logged with transaction ID TXN-884521 and will be 
</span><span>reviewed within 24 hours. You will receive a follow-up directly.
</span><span>
</span><span>I apologize for the inconvenience and appreciate your patience. Is 
</span><span>there anything else I can help you with in the meantime?
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>No that's fine, thank you.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>You're welcome. We will be in touch shortly. Have a great day.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Analysis</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Element </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Notes </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-header-row"></span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-line"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Tone </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Empathetic opening, professional throughout </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Tier 1 steps followed </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Yes - restart attempted before escalating </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Information collected </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Username, transaction ID, timing </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Escalation triggered </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Yes - items missing after troubleshooting </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Promises made </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> None - only timeframe provided </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Outcome </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Correctly escalated to billing specialist </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
