          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="text-text-500 font-small p-3.5 pb-0">markdown</div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-markdown" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;"><span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">#</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Sample Conversation - Immediate Escalation</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Scenario</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>A player contacts support claiming their account was accessed by 
</span><span>someone else and in-game items are missing.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Conversation</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Someone hacked into my account. I just logged in and all my resources 
</span><span>are gone. I did not give anyone my password. Please help.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Hi, I am sorry to hear this happened. I understand this is very 
</span><span>upsetting and I want to assure you this is being taken seriously.
</span><span>
</span><span>To protect your account right now, please do the following immediately:
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Change your password from a secure device.
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> If your account is linked to a Google or Facebook account, 
</span></span><span>   change those passwords as well.
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Check for any apps or services connected to your account and 
</span></span><span>   revoke access to any you do not recognize.
</span><span>
</span><span>Have you been able to change your password already?
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Yes I just changed it. But my resources are still gone.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Thank you for acting quickly. I am escalating this to our security 
</span><span>team immediately as this requires specialist investigation. They will 
</span><span>review your account activity and look into the missing resources.
</span><span>
</span><span>To help them investigate, could you confirm:
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Your Player ID or in-game username
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Approximately when you last had normal access to your account
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> What device you normally play on
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>My username is StarCommander7. I last played yesterday evening, 
</span><span>everything was fine. I play on iPhone 13.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Thank you. I have logged all of this and your case is being escalated 
</span><span>as high priority to our security team. You can expect a follow-up 
</span><span>within 4 hours.
</span><span>
</span><span>Please do not share your new password with anyone, including support 
</span><span>staff. We will never ask for it.
</span><span>
</span><span>I am sorry this happened and we will do everything we can to 
</span><span>investigate. Is there anything else you need right now?
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Player:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>No, just please fix this as soon as possible.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>Understood. Our team will be in touch shortly. Thank you for your 
</span><span>patience.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Analysis</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Element </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Notes </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-header-row"></span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span class="token token table table-line" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-line">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-line"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Tone </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Urgent acknowledgment, calm and reassuring </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Tier 1 steps followed </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Immediate security advice given first </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Information collected </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Username, timeline, device </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Escalation triggered </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Yes - immediately, high priority </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Promises made </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> None beyond timeframe and investigation </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Outcome </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Correctly routed to security team </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
